availability.p: Avtorske pravice za to izdajo urejata Pogodba o zbiranju in uporabi besedilnega korpusa v okviru projekta Sporazumevanje v slovenskem jeziku in Pogodba o zbiranju in uporabi besedilnega korpusa v okviru projekta Nadgradnja korpusov Gigafida, Kres, ccGigafida in ccKres. Za dostop do korpusnih podatkov je treba poslati prošnjo na naslov: info@cjvt.si.

The copyright for this edition is governed by the Agreement on Collection and Use of the Text Corpus under the framework of the Communication in Slovene project and by the Agreement on Collection and Use of the Text Corpus under the framework of the Upgrading of the Gigafida, Kres, ccGigafida and ccKres Corpora project. Request to access corpus data can be sent to: info@cjvt.si.
